<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>﴿وَالَّذِينَ يَمْكُرُونَ السَّيِّئَاتِ﴾ <span style="color:#707070">[فاطر: ١٠]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٨٦ -<span style="color:#006d98"> قال ابن عباس:</span> هم أصحاب الرياء <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>﴿وَجَاءَكُمُ النَّذِيرُ﴾ <span style="color:#707070">[فاطر: ٣٧]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣٨٧ -<span style="color:#006d98"> قال زيد بن علي:</span> القرآن <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
